ChangeLog
---------

[2014-09-05]
* Release version 1.0.1.
* Update dist.ini to ensure README.md is included in tarball.
* Add Changes file.

[2014-09-05]
* Release version 1.0.0.
* Add initial dzil dist.ini, remove cruft.
* Update perldocs for 1.0.0 release.

[2010-04-29]
* Bump version to 0.9.1.
* Add environment support, including to applied dir.

[2010-02-28]
* Bump version to 0.9.
* Update perldocs for file-based version.
* Other changes to file-based version.
* Update tests to file-based versions.
* Convert from database-based tracking to file-based.

[2008-02-23]
* Bump version to 0.6.
* Fix buglet in testdir location.
* Updates to MANIFEST.
* Add perldocs on new statement filtering.
* Add statement filtering tests; add -s flag for stmt reporting.

[2007-11-22]
* Bump version to 0.5.
* Add a filter_statement method to DBIx::Delta; bump version to 0.5.
* Remove leftover t02_base/delta.db.

[2007-11-22]
* Bump version to 0.4.
* Add real test case (02_base.t).

[2007-07-31]
* Bump version to 0.3.1.
* Fix quiet buglet.
* Add -q quiet argument.

[2007-07-31]
* Bump version to 0.3.
* Reenable semicolon escaping inside single quotes.

[2007-06-08]
* Add noop support to Delta; comment out semicolon escaping temporarily.
* Initial import.

